Runyenjes MP Cecily Mbarire has said Embu residents need a tough, go-getter career politician - like her - to develop the county. She described her opponents as &ldquo;people seeking shelter from retirement&rdquo;. Speaking in Embu town on Monday, Mbarire said, &ldquo;I can go anywhere to seek resources for the people of Embu without fear because I have experience.&rdquo;